      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i just tripped while running and my ankle is super swollen. i cant really walk on it right now but it doesnt feel like it's broken or anything, just really painful. do u think i should just do the rice thing (rest, ice, compression, elevation) for a few days and see if it gets better?",
