      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'm just worried about the cost of an ER or urgent care visit if it's nothing major. do u think i could just take some ibuprofen and keep icing it for like 3 or 4 days to see how it goes? i'd rather avoid the doctor if i can just manage the swelling at home.",
